page.title: 02MY HOUSE IN KEELBY
page.content: I am an eleven year old girl living in Keelby.I am a pupil at Keelby County Primary School.My name is Natalie Hollowday.I enjoy tennis,netball and rambling in woods and fields in the area.I like animals and enjoy looking after dogs.There is a dancing school which is very exciting, but hard work.Also I go to Guides and I am in a choir at Keelby Parish Church. I live in a semi-detached council house which is about 30 years old.My mum and dad live with me,but I have no brothers or sisters.I have many animals like dogs,guinea-pigs and goldfish.We have quite a big garden in which my dad grows vegetables like carrots,onions and potatoes.I grow flowers with my dad and mum, as we all enjoy gardening.My dad is on the dole so he spends much time in the garden.
